title: [FSX/P3D] Mallorca Highres Scenery 50 cm
description:
Instruccions:

You only have to add the "Mallorca HighRes 50cm" folder as a new scenery in your scenery librery.

Extra information:

It's included Mallorca Mesh from "MESH FSX LOD13 BALEARES2" March/2013 (airhispania)

As well, I've included the autogen "16 Islas Baleares v2.1.4" April/2015 (airhispania)

Advanced users: 

If you want to use other mesh, you can delete the file "Mallorca HighRes 50cmsceneryMDT05-ISLAS-BALEARES.bgl"

If you don't want to see the autogen, you can delete "texture" folder completely and 

also the "autogen_objetos_644_X_XXX" files from the "scenery" folder.
